text.content: Slidzo is a subscription-based Saas that offers different packages and premium accounts for companies and individuals. The subscription fees account for 60% of the revenue.
* Average rates are not final prices as they might be subject to change depending on clients, events and template types

text.content:
Writing too much in a slide deck will lose your audience’s attention.

If you have a long trail of thoughts, separate them into digestible paragraphs — or even better, multiple slides.

Like this paragraph. Isn’t this nice to read?

This layout is two text columns, but this is also a great place for a table, chart, or image.

Or how about a numbered list?

1. Here is an item that may be extended up to three lines. Anything beyond that may be too information dense for this single entry.

2. Here is the second item that has two sentences. Together, they still don’t extend beyond three lines of text.

text.content:
Writing too much in a slide deck will lose your audience’s attention.

If you have a long trail of thoughts, separate them into digestible paragraphs — or even better, multiple slides.

Like this paragraph. Isn’t this nice to read?

Do you have design needs for your presentations?

Zacht Studios specializes in investor presentations.

We’ve crafted investor pitch decks for some of your favorite companies from every industry, and have supported startups in raising more than $1.24B to date.

Avoid abbreviations and acronyms. It’s always great to write out what you are trying to say with clarity.

If you are going to use acronyms, define them with their first appearance in text.

For example, “Net Promoter Score (NPS)”

text.content:
Writing too much in a slide deck will lose your audience’s attention.

If you have a long trail of thoughts, separate them into digestible paragraphs — or even better, multiple slides.

Like this paragraph. Isn’t this nice to read?

text.content:
Right-click app screen to Edit in Photoshop!

Switch over to Assets in the bottom-left corner (Shift + Command/Control + Y), right-click a document Color, and select Edit to change the colors across your entire presentation.

You can change the document fonts in the Assets panel too.

text.content:
Right-click app screen to Edit in Photoshop!

Switch over to Assets in the bottom-left corner (Shift + Command/Control + Y), right-click a document Color, and select Edit to change the colors across your entire presentation.

You can change the document fonts in the Assets panel too.

text.content:
Vous avez probablement un emploi du temps pour vos cours, mais si vous avez du mal à vous concentrer, prenez une pause de 5 minutes, faites-le simplement savoir à votre professeur. 

Prenez soin de votre esprit si vous 
avez besoin d'une pause.

text.content: Exprimez-vous et demandez de l'aide si besoin.
Il ne sert à rien de stresser quand les choses deviennent difficiles. Posez des questions à vos parents, contactez votre enseignant, ou demandez de l'aide à vos camarades de classe.
L'aide est toujours là quand on la demande.
